The memorial service for slain rapper Kiernan Forbes,  popularly known as AKA,  is being held at the Sandton Convention Centre in Johannesburg on Friday  afternoon. AKA and his friend and former manager Tebello “Tibz” Motsoane were gunned down in Durban on Friday last week. TimesLIVE Support independent journalism by subscribing to the Sunday Times. Just R20 for the first month.